article_id:1227,category_name:News,title_name:A New Summon Showcase Is Now Live!,image_path:,message:<div>A new Summon Showcase went live <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1586757600"></span>!</div><div><br></div><div>Featured adventurers and dragons currently have boosted appearance rates.</div><div><br></div><div>Newly featured adventurers and dragons:</div><div><br></div><div>■Adventurer</div><div>5★ Lazry (water/axe)</div><div>4★ Gauld (water/lance)</div><div><br></div><div>■Dragon</div><div>5★ Gaibhne &amp; Creidhne (water)</div><div><br></div><div>・For information about other featured adventurers and dragons, tap Summon on the in-game footer menu, then select Appearance Rates and check the Appearance Rates section.</div><div><br></div><div>Availability period for featured summons:</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1586757600"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1587362340"></span></div><div><br></div><div>Get a closer look at some of the newly featured adventurers and dragons below.</div><div><br></div><div>Featured adventurer:</div><div>
