				<div>
					Deals water damage to enemies directly ahead,<br>and inflicts frostbite. If this skill is used when<br>the user is in high power mode, a variant called<br>Hyper Smithy Spin will be used instead.<br>Hyper Smithy Spin deals water damage<br>to the target and nearby enemies,<br>and increases the damage dealt by<br>the user's next skill by 20%.
				</div>
			</dd>
	
			<dt>
				<span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/20cad8e4fa011f9a61e0e16c16dc42ba2.png"></span>
				<span>Smithy Arm: Forge Mode</span>
			</dt>
			<dd>
				<div>
					Increases the entire team's strength by 15%<br>for 15 seconds, and their critical rate by 10%<br>for 15 seconds. If this skill is used when the user<br>is in high power mode, a variant called<br>Smithy Arm: Power Mode will be used instead.<br>Smithy Arm: Power Mode deals water damage<br>to the target and nearby enemies, and<br>immediately readies the Smithy Spin<br>(or Hyper Smithy Spin) skill for use.
